description:
PANDA is a token launched by PANDALAND with applications regarding:

Animation feature movie 《Pandamonium》, Pandaland Ice Cream Store , Web series 《Mary Sue & Jack Sue II》, Gaming 《Crypto Panda》and 《Panda Theme Park 》.

So whether its buying ice-cream, watching movies, downloading videos, having fun at a theme park, buying animation merchandise or playing games etc.

PANDA has got you covered!
